The paper discusses inference mechanisms for deductive databases, which are a subfield of database management systems. Therefore, cs.DB is the most likely category. The paper also mentions rule-based systems and query optimization, which are topics related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). The paper also presents a new version of the soft consequence operator, which is a mathematical concept related to data structures (cs.DS) and programming languages (cs.PL).
